//! * <code>[std::iter]::[FromIterator]</code>.
//!
//! The prelude used in Rust 2024, [`std::prelude::rust_2024`], includes all of the above,
//! and in addition re-exports:
//!
//! * <code>[std::future]::{[Future], [IntoFuture]}</code>.
