//! [`std::prelude::rust_2018`]: rust_2018
//! [`std::prelude::rust_2021`]: rust_2021
//! [`std::prelude::rust_2024`]: rust_2024
//! [std::result]: crate::result
//! [std::slice]: crate::slice
